description: Intercontinental Gold and Metals Ltd. engages in the gold and metals trading business in Canada and Bolivia. It is involved in the gold refining; and physical commodities marketing and trading operations. The company was formerly known as Geodex Minerals Ltd. and changed its name to Intercontinental Gold and Metals Ltd. in November 2017. Intercontinental Gold and Metals Ltd. was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
